Package com.castinfo.devops.robotest

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PageObject
    This class is used to PageObject/PageObject test orienting.
    RobotestExecutionContext
    This class brings acces to execution context of ROBOTEST Suites and Cases, buildin and stoping all that objects needed and make posible to retrive this load objects internally throught Suite - Case - Steps execution.
    StepInterceptor
    This class implement interceptor of PageObject/PageObject to provide proxy for automate reporting purposes.
    SuiteContext
    This class contains context object needed for Robotest Suite execution, for example, Report, Selenium Web Driver and Selenium associated Dockers.
    TestCase
    Suite classes extends this class to build context of Suite, Case and Step PageObjects/PageFragments context.
    TestContext
    Test context object properties.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    StepStatus
    Enumeration of posible status results of robotest execution validations.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    RobotestException
    Generic error exception wrapper for robotest.
